main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Lincolnwood, Illinois on 17 June 1963.
interesting points: The object was described as round like a disk and silver in color., The manner of observation was noted as waiting for a bus., The sighting occurred around 12:25 AM on 18 June 1963., The report indicated that there was insufficient data to establish the reality of the sighting., The document is a page from a Project Blue Book record card and does not contain any photographs.
